Safety and efficacy of teriflunomide in paediatric multiple sclerosis 
(TERIKIDS): a multicentre, double-blind, phase 3, randomised, placebo-controlled 
trial.

Chitnis T(1), Banwell B(2), Kappos L(3), Arnold DL(4), Gücüyener K(5), Deiva 
