756. BMC Cancer. 2021 Nov 20;21(1):1250. doi: 10.1186/s12885-021-08875-5.

Capsular extension at ultrasound is associated with lateral lymph node 
metastasis in patients with papillary thyroid carcinoma: a retrospective study.

